{%- comment -%}
  ============================================================================
  Design System · Section: Sportart-Umschalter (fs-sport-switcher)
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Schlanke Leiste mit Aufklapp-Dropdown zum Wechseln zwischen den Sportwelten.
  Wird global in der Header-Gruppe angezeigt.

  Aktive Welt-Erkennung (wie bei der Kategorie-Leiste):
    1. Welt-Seite (/pages/welt-tischtennis …) oder
    2. eine aktive Unterkategorie der Sportart (z. B. /collections/holzer).
  Grundlage ist das Menü (Top-Ebene mit Unterpunkten).

  Persistenz: Die zuletzt gewählte Sportart wird per localStorage gemerkt und
  bleibt auch auf neutralen Seiten (Startseite, Warenkorb, Suche) sichtbar –
  bis eine andere Sportart gewählt wird. Dropdown selbst ist CSS-only
  (details/summary); das kleine Skript aktualisiert nur das Label.
  ============================================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign accent = section.settings.accent_color | default: '#486A8F'
  assign uid = section.id | replace: '_', '' | replace: '-', ''
  assign default_label = section.settings.default_label | default: 'Sportwelt wählen'
  assign path = request.path
  assign menu = linklists[section.settings.menu]

  comment
    1) Sportwelt über die Welt-Seite erkennen.
  endcomment
  assign current_world = null
  for link in menu.links
    if link.links.size > 0 and link.url != '/' and link.url != blank
      if path == link.url or path contains link.url
        assign current_world = link.url
      endif
    endif
  endfor

  comment
    2) Sonst über eine aktive Unterkategorie (Kollektionsseite) erkennen.
  endcomment
  unless current_world
    for link in menu.links
      if link.links.size > 0
        for sub in link.links
          if sub.url != blank and sub.url != '/'
            assign sub_prefix = sub.url | append: '/'
            if path == sub.url or path contains sub_prefix
              assign current_world = link.url
            endif
          endif
        endfor
      endif
    endfor
  endunless

  comment
    Passenden Block (Sportart) zur erkannten Welt finden → Label + Link.
    current_sport_link bleibt leer, wenn die aktuelle Seite keiner Sportart
    zugeordnet ist (z. B. Courts, Standorte) – dann greift die Persistenz.
  endcomment
  assign current_label = default_label
  assign current_sport_link = ''
  for block in section.blocks
    if current_world and block.settings.link == current_world
      assign current_label = block.settings.label
      assign current_sport_link = block.settings.link
    endif
  endfor
-%}

{%- style -%}
  .fs-sw2--{{ uid }} { --fs-sw2-accent: var(--fs-sport-accent, {{ accent }}); }
{%- endstyle -%}

<style>
  .fs-sw2 { border-block: 1px solid rgba(128,128,128,.16); background: var(--fs-sw2-bg, transparent); }
  .fs-sw2__inner { max-width: var(--page-width, 1400px); margin-inline: auto; padding: .5rem var(--page-margin, 2rem); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .75rem; justify-content: var(--fs-sw2-justify, center); }
  .fs-sw2__label { font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .04em; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: .7; }

  .fs-sw2__dd { position: relative; }
  .fs-sw2__summary {
    list-style: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem;
    padding: .5rem .9rem; border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid rgba(128,128,128,.35);
    font-weight: 600; font-size: .95rem; user-select: none;
  }
  .fs-sw2__summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .fs-sw2__summary .fs-sw2__dot { width: .55rem; height: .55rem; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--fs-sw2-accent); }
  .fs-sw2__summary .fs-sw2__caret { width: 1rem; height: 1rem; transition: transform .15s ease; }
  .fs-sw2__dd[open] .fs-sw2__caret { transform: rotate(180deg); }
  .fs-sw2__summary:focus-visible { outline: 3px solid var(--fs-sw2-accent); outline-offset: 2px; }

  .fs-sw2__menu {
    position: absolute; z-index: 40; top: calc(100% + .4rem); left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    min-width: 15rem; padding: .4rem; border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--fs-sw2-menu-bg, #14181c); color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(8,12,18,.35);
    display: grid; gap: 2px;
  }
  .fs-sw2__item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .6rem; padding: .6rem .7rem; border-radius: 9px; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; font-weight: 600; }
  .fs-sw2__item:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); }
  .fs-sw2__item[aria-current="page"] { background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--fs-sw2-accent) 30%, transparent); }
  .fs-sw2__item .fs-sw2__ico { width: 1.4rem; height: 1.4rem; color: var(--fs-sw2-accent); flex: none; }
  .fs-sw2__item .fs-sw2__sub { display: block; font-weight: 400; font-size: .8rem; opacity: .7; }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .fs-sw2__caret { transition: none; } }
</style>

<div id="fs-sw2-{{ uid }}" class="fs-sw2 fs-sw2--{{ uid }}" data-current-link="{{ current_sport_link }}"{% if section.settings.align == 'left' %} style="--fs-sw2-justify:flex-start;"{% endif %}>
  <div class="fs-sw2__inner">
    {%- if section.settings.label_text != blank -%}<span class="fs-sw2__label">{{ section.settings.label_text }}</span>{%- endif -%}
    <details class="fs-sw2__dd">
      <summary class="fs-sw2__summary">
        <span class="fs-sw2__dot"></span>
        <span class="fs-sw2__current">{{ current_label }}</span>
        <svg class="fs-sw2__caret" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </summary>
      <div class="fs-sw2__menu">
        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          {%- liquid
            assign lnk = block.settings.link | default: ''
            assign is_current = false
            if current_sport_link != '' and lnk == current_sport_link
              assign is_current = true
            endif
          -%}
          <a class="fs-sw2__item" href="{{ lnk | default: '#' }}" data-sport-link="{{ lnk }}" data-sport-label="{{ block.settings.label | escape }}"{% if is_current %} aria-current="page"{% endif %}>
            <span class="fs-sw2__ico">
              {%- case block.settings.icon -%}
                {%- when 'padel' -%}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M9 14l-3 7M12 15v6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                {%- when 'pickleball' -%}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="10" cy="7" r="1" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="14" cy="7" r="1" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="1" fill="currentColor"/><path d="M12 14v7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                {%- when 'tabletennis' -%}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 13h16M6 13c0-4 3-7 7-7s5 2 5 4-2 3-4 3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M8 13l1 7M16 13l-1 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                {%- else -%}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
              {%- endcase -%}
            </span>
            <span>{{ block.settings.label }}{%- if block.settings.sub != blank -%}<span class="fs-sw2__sub">{{ block.settings.sub }}</span>{%- endif -%}</span>
          </a>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  (function () {
    var root = document.getElementById('fs-sw2-{{ uid }}');
    if (!root) return;
    var KEY = 'fs-sport-world';
    var labelEl = root.querySelector('.fs-sw2__current');
    var items = root.querySelectorAll('.fs-sw2__item');
    var serverLink = root.getAttribute('data-current-link') || '';

    function save(link, label) {
      try { localStorage.setItem(KEY, JSON.stringify({ link: link, label: label })); } catch (e) {}
    }
    function markActive(link) {
      items.forEach(function (a) {
        if (a.getAttribute('data-sport-link') === link) { a.setAttribute('aria-current', 'page'); }
        else { a.removeAttribute('aria-current'); }
      });
    }

    if (serverLink) {
      // Aktuelle Seite gehört zu einer Sportart → als zuletzt gewählt merken.
      items.forEach(function (a) {
        if (a.getAttribute('data-sport-link') === serverLink) {
          save(serverLink, a.getAttribute('data-sport-label'));
        }
      });
    } else {
      // Neutrale Seite → zuletzt gewählte Sportart wiederherstellen.
      var raw = null;
      try { raw = localStorage.getItem(KEY); } catch (e) {}
      if (raw) {
        try {
          var s = JSON.parse(raw);
          if (s && s.label && s.link) {
            if (labelEl) { labelEl.textContent = s.label; }
            markActive(s.link);
          }
        } catch (e) {}
      }
    }

    // Auswahl im Dropdown sofort merken (Navigation bestätigt sie danach ohnehin).
    items.forEach(function (a) {
      a.addEventListener('click', function () {
        save(a.getAttribute('data-sport-link'), a.getAttribute('data-sport-label'));
      });
    });
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Sportart-Umschalter",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "fs-section",
  "settings": [
    { "type": "link_list", "id": "menu", "label": "Menü (zur Sport-Erkennung)", "default": "main-menu" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "label_text", "label": "Label davor", "default": "Sportwelt:" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "default_label", "label": "Standard-Text (keine Welt aktiv)", "default": "Sportwelt wählen" },
    {
      "type": "select", "id": "align", "label": "Ausrichtung",
      "options": [ { "value": "center", "label": "Zentriert" }, { "value": "left", "label": "Links" } ],
      "default": "center"
    },
    { "type": "color", "id": "accent_color", "label": "Akzentfarbe (Futurespin-Blau)", "default": "#486A8F" }
  ],
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "world",
      "name": "Sportwelt",
      "settings": [
        {
          "type": "select", "id": "icon", "label": "Icon",
          "options": [
            { "value": "tabletennis", "label": "Tischtennis" },
            { "value": "padel", "label": "Padel" },
            { "value": "pickleball", "label": "Pickleball" },
            { "value": "none", "label": "Keins" }
          ],
          "default": "tabletennis"
        },
        { "type": "text", "id": "label", "label": "Titel", "default": "Tischtennis" },
        { "type": "text", "id": "sub", "label": "Untertext (optional)" },
        { "type": "url", "id": "link", "label": "Link zur Welt-Seite" }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Sportart-Umschalter",
      "blocks": [
        { "type": "world", "settings": { "icon": "tabletennis", "label": "Tischtennis" } },
        { "type": "world", "settings": { "icon": "padel", "label": "Padel" } },
        { "type": "world", "settings": { "icon": "pickleball", "label": "Pickleball" } }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
